item.title: Positives of this Project
item.dc:creator: bxs5834
item.content:encoded:
• This Project is helping us elevate our Web Development skills by using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and PHP.
  • How to work in a team is another great aspect of this project.
  • To know how a full stack web developer works and the process involving. Great insight to real world projects.
  • Learning minute details which helps us stand out.
  • Using of Wordpress is also one of the things that is new to us.
  • How to deploy our work on Cloud is also essential and is a part of our project.

item.title: Negatives of this Project
item.dc:creator: bxs5834
item.content:encoded:
• Some part of the website is developed using Wordpress while other pages are not.
  • We cannot experiment much since most of the project has constant parameters and design.
  • It is not interactive.
  • Some of the requirements are not up to date or does not sync well.
  • A bit of discrepancy between instructions being told and the instructions give. Which creates a bit of confusion.

item.title: How can we Improve!
item.dc:creator: bxs5834
item.content:encoded:
• More creativity option should be provided.
  • The User Interface could be improved a bit.
  • Instructions could be a bit more clear.
  • Modern techniques can be implemented to elevate the user experience.
